          "subtitle": "Shaping Play Through Procedural Generation",
          "slidecontent": "• AI tools now help create vast amounts of in-game content automatically\n• Procedural generation builds levels, characters, and quests without manual design for each one\n• Faster, cheaper\n• Players encounter unique experiences shaped by algorithms rather than hand-crafted decisions\n• Understanding how this works helps you spot the risks before they affect your players"
