          "number": 5,
          "slidetitle": "Balancing Creativity and Control",
          "subtitle": "When AI Creativity Needs Human Oversight",
          "slidecontent": "• AI can produce unexpected or off-brand content without proper guardrails in place\n• Human review catches tone, cultural sensitivity, and narrative consistency issues\n• Essential for quality control\n• Procedural generation left unchecked risks flooding players with repetitive or incoherent experiences\n• Simple approval workflows help teams stay in control without slowing down production"
